{"tid":1765382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊星期六係「歡樂滿東華」，記得罷睇罷捐，咪益東華三院","createTime":"2019-12-01T22:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T01:59:16.000Z","uid":290404,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"33bce8d781d180e3402924af65469e774c6ebec7","tid":1765382,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T22:46:17.000Z","msg":"唔講盧幹庭中學對中學生記過單野，之前李東海小學，害死左林麗棠老師，東華三院除左炒鬼左個住精神病房既校長之外仲有乜野做過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有東華三院屬下中小學出名訓導嚴厲，前兩年甲寅年中學有中五學生俾訓導主任逼死，搞到要開死因庭<br />\n<br />\n東華管理層個個都係藍，尤其而家果位施榮忻主席，都係福建幫之一，係香港福建社團聯會董事會副主席！迫Ｄ學生去支那洗腦團，唔准佢地罷課，唔准佢地係學校整連儂牆！<br />\n<br />\n為左受壓迫既學生同老師，大家應該罷捐東華三院 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，由得班奶共總理自己圍威喂！<br />\n<br />\n總之都係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷捐東華三院，拒絕收睇歡樂滿東華</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1799db20885d03bf4b537fb0cfe8ee5b9c98cea4","tid":1765382,"uid":179729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T22:47:58.000Z","msg":"無捐好耐<br />\n<br />\n捐星火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804a4e95dcc3b456c27c0bebd179b3f9d5ef15f2","tid":1765382,"uid":42435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T22:54:38.000Z","msg":"唔捐，顯示黃色經濟圈威力"},{"pid":"311cc2c356518acc18a88c6e93e9e6f8e5c7054d","tid":1765382,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T22:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src